      },
      "rationale": "CFD-predicted normalized hemolysis index compared against in-vitro MIH measurements at all five operating points. Agreement within ± 11.4% (worst case: 4.5 L/min @ 4500 RPM, 11.4% over-prediction). Systematic bias across five points: 4.2%. Combined uncertainty intervals (95% CI from Monte Carlo) overlap experimental uncertainty bounds at all points. Gradation 4 criteria met."
