        "description": "Validation experiments must use the same FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry as the COU device; at least 4 of 5 COU operating points must be directly tested (not interpolated); blood analog fluid properties must be within 10% of bovine blood rheology at 37 °C."
      },
      "rationale": "Validation experiments conducted on the FDA-specified generic centrifugal pump geometry (STL file SHA-256 verified against COU model geometry). All five COU2 operating points directly tested — no interpolation required. Bovine blood viscosity at 37 °C within 6% of modeled Carreau-Yasuda parameters. Geometry, boundary conditions, and fluid properties are directly representative of the COU. Gradation 4 confirmed."
