      "rationale": "All simulations converged with residual reduction ≥ 5 orders of magnitude (continuity, momentum, turbulence). Mass imbalance < 0.003% at all operating points. Hemolysis index stabilized within 0.2% change over final 500 iterations. Double-precision arithmetic used throughout. Iterative error contribution to total error budget: < 0.1%. Gradation 4 exceeds required Gradation 3."
